    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Adjustable tables, with ledges at the back and sides, used by persons in bed, usually for eating or writing. Also may refer to tables at the side of a bed. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
